<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Application Order Ackowleadgement Template</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Poppins' , sans-serif; font-size:14px;color:#302c2b; line-height:2;">
    <div class="rt-tb-scrl">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>
            @*@if ((Model.Ordertype == "change of project" || Model.Ordertype == "enhancement") && Model.isMSPhd == true && Model.TypeofAppointment == "Selection")
            {
                if (Model.Ordertype == "enhancement" && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.FillFields))
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to the @Model.FillFields request for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                }
                else if (Model.Ordertype == "enhancement")
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to the enhancement request for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    <p>This is with reference to the change of project request for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                }
                <p> The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking </li>
                    <li>Dean IC&SR approval</li>
                    <li>Offer Release </li>
                </ol>
            }*@
            @if (Model.Ordertype == "change of project")
            {

                <p>This is with reference to the @Model.Ordertype request received for  <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName, @Model.TypeofAppointment</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                <p>The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Committee approval</li>
                    <li>Offer Release</li>
                </ol>
                <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the offer letter is 7 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            }
            else if (Model.Ordertype == "extension" && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.FillFields))
            {
                <p>This is with reference to the @Model.FillFields request received for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName, @Model.TypeofAppointment</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                <p>The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Committee approval</li>
                    <li>Offer Release</li>
                </ol>
                <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the offer letter is 7 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            }
            else if (Model.Ordertype == "extension")
            {
                <p>This is with reference to the term extension request received for <b>@Model.PersonName, @Model.DesignationName</b>  with effect from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> , under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of Rs. @Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under process. </p>
                <p>The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Extension order release</li>
                </ol>
                <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the extension order is 5 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            }
            else if (Model.Ordertype == "enhancement" && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.FillFields))
            {
                <p>This is with reference to the @Model.FillFields request received for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, for the  post of <b>@Model.DesignationName, @Model.TypeofAppointment</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate to @Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of salary Rs.@Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
                <p>The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Committee approval</li>
                    <li>Offer Release</li>
                </ol>
                <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the offer letter is 7 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            }
            else if (Model.Ordertype == "enhancement")
            {
                <p>This is with reference to the salary enhancement request received for  <b>@Model.PersonName, @Model.DesignationName</b> in the project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> is under process. </p>
                <p>The following will be the next steps from our end</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Enhancement order release</li>
                </ol>
                <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the enhancement order is 5 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            }
            <p>For any queries, kindly send an email to <a href="mailto:to icsrrecruitment3@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank">icsrrecruitment3@imail.iitm.ac.in </a>/<a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in</a> and we will get back to you at the earliest.</p>
            <p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px;">
                @Model.DAName<br>
                Project Recruitment<br>
                Centre for IC&SR<br>
                IIT Madras<br>
                *This is a system generated email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
